text: Cemetery Miséricorde is one of the major cemeteries in Nantes, France. It is located in the Hauts-Pavés - Saint-Félix district. It was opened in 1793 and over 10,000 graves have been placed their between then and 2010. ==Gallery== Cimetière Miséricorde Nantes - Philippe Gengembre - Buste.jpg|Bust of Philippe Gengembre W0170-BureauLeon 1837-1900 57061.JPG Cimetière Miséricorde Nantes - Louis Babin-Chevaye - Médaillon.jpg Nantes - Cimetière Miséricorde - Tombe de Cambronne.JPG|Grave of Pierre Cambronne Category:Cemeteries in France Category:Nantes
